- "Favorite locations" are those marked as favorites by users;
- "More than one event" means the location has hosted at least two events.

- 'Three most recent landmarks' refers to the top three events for each user based on the event date and time in descending order;
- 'Traveler's name' is the concatenation of the user's first name and last name;
- 'Date and time of the visit' is the event date and event time;
- 'Location of the landmark' includes the location name, latitude, and longitude.

